Original repo by Harkirat - https://github.com/100xdevs-cohort-2/week-13/tree/main/backend

1. npm create hono@latest
2. Create routes in index.ts
3. Initialize Prisma
4. create Schema's or Models in schema.prisma
5. Make prisma pooling + postgresql Links and attach in files.
    postgresQL url in - .env files and (fecth from console.aiven.io)
    Prisma pooling url in - Wrangler.toml files (fecth from console.aiven.io)
6. Migrate the prisma - 
                    npx prisma migrate dev --name init_schema
7. Generate the Prisma Client - 
                    npx prisma generate --no-engine
8. Add the accelrate extension - 
                    npm i @prisma/extension-accelerate
9. initialize jwt for tokens.
10. middlewares.  starts with- Router.use("",async (c, next)=>{ logic ...})
. 
.
.
deploy project on CLOUDFLARE

11. Initialize the ZOD adn implement it to the project, build a new folder apart from from backend and frontend for zod 
    and write all zod code in the dufferent.